ti Cabinet}}\n{{Prime ministers of Italy}}\n{{European Commissioner for Competition}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Monti, Mario}}\n[[Category:1943 births]]\n[[Category:20th-century Italian politicians]]\n[[Category:20th-century economists]]\n[[Category:21st-century Italian politicians]]\n[[Category:Bocconi University faculty]]\n[[Category:Civic Choice politicians]]\n[[Category:Independent politicians in Italy]]\n[[Category:Coca-Cola people]]\n[[Category:Eurofederalism]]\n[[Category:Italian economists]]\n[[Category:Italian European Commissioners]]\n[[Category:Italian Life Senators]]\n[[Category:Italian people of Argentine descent]]\n[[Category:Goldman Sachs people]]\n[[Category:Members of the Steering Committee of the Bilderberg Group]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Varese]]\n[[Category:Prime Ministers of Italy]]\n[[Category:Finance ministers of Italy]]\n[[Category:University of Turin faculty]]\n[[Category:Yale University alumni]]\n[[Category:Italian Roman Catholics]]\n", "name_user": "77.134.227.100", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mario_Monti"}
